@startuml seq_15_vote_on_content
title Sequence Diagram: UC-15 Vote on Content

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Vote Controller" as Controller
participant "Vote Service" as Service
participant "Target Repo" as TargetRepo
participant "Vote Repo" as VoteRepo

User -> Frontend: Click Upvote or Downvote
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/votes {target_id, target_type, value}
Controller -> Service: Submit Vote (targetID, type, value)
Service -> TargetRepo: Verify target exists & is visible
TargetRepo --> Service: Target is valid

Service -> VoteRepo: Find existing vote by User & Target
VoteRepo --> Service: Existing vote state (if any)

alt New vote
    Service -> VoteRepo: Create new vote record
else Change vote (Up to Down, Down to Up)
    Service -> VoteRepo: Update vote record
else Remove vote (Click same button again)
    Service -> VoteRepo: Delete vote record
end

Service -> TargetRepo: Recalculate & update total score
TargetRepo --> Service: New score updated
Service --> Controller: Updated Vote Totals
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Update vote count UI
@enduml